</div>

## Features
- Track and log your daily food intake.
- Get detailed nutritional information for each food item.
- Set nutrition goals and monitor your progress.
- Search and discover new food options.
- View comprehensive nutrition reports and statistics.

## Installation
1. Clone the repository:
    ```
    git clone https://github.com/your-username/food-nutrition-app.git
    ```
2. Navigate to the project directory:
    ```
    cd food-nutrition-app
    ```
3. Install the required dependencies:
    ```
    pip install -r requirements.txt
    ```
4. Run the application:
    ```
    python app.py
    ```

## Usage
1. Open the application in your web browser by visiting `http://localhost:5000`.
2. Create an account or log in if you already have one.
3. Start tracking your food intake by adding items to your daily log.
4. Explore the app's features to view nutritional information, set goals, and analyze your data.

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Flask (Web framework)
- SQLite (Database)
- HTML/CSS/JavaScript (Frontend)

